When selecting individual entities (e.g., countries, people) from tables that include both entity rows AND summary/aggregate rows (e.g., "total", "overall"), always pre-filter the table to exclude aggregate rows before selecting your answer. Aggregate rows are not valid entities and may cause nonsensical outputs if treated as such.

